datasets.name: 15b378d8
queryLines:
SELECT
  a.name as artist,
  al.name as album,
  al.release_year,
  ROUND(AVG(ra.rating), 1) AS avg_rating
FROM
  music.silver_album al
    JOIN music.silver_artist a
      ON al.artist_id = a.id
    JOIN music.silver_member_rating ra
      ON al.id = ra.album_id
GROUP BY
  a.name,
  al.name,
  al.release_year
ORDER BY
  avg_rating DESC;

datasets.name: 19d9076c
queryLines:
SELECT
  CASE
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1955 AND 1959 THEN '1955-1959'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1960 AND 1964 THEN '1960-1964'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1965 AND 1969 THEN '1965-1969'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1970 AND 1974 THEN '1970-1974'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1975 AND 1979 THEN '1975-1979'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1980 AND 1984 THEN '1980-1984'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1985 AND 1989 THEN '1985-1989'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1990 AND 1994 THEN '1990-1994'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1995 AND 1999 THEN '1995-1999'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2004 THEN '2000-2004'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 2005 AND 2009 THEN '2005-2009'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 2010 AND 2014 THEN '2010-2014'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 2015 AND 2019 THEN '2015-2019'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 2020 AND 2024 THEN '2020-2024'
    ELSE 'Other'
  END AS year_bucket,
  AVG(ra.rating) AS avg_rating
FROM
  workspace.music.silver_album al
JOIN 
  workspace.music.silver_member_rating ra
ON 
  al.id = ra.album_id
GROUP BY
  year_bucket
ORDER BY
  year_bucket;

datasets.name: 62bff10c
queryLines:
SELECT
  CASE
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1955 AND 1959 THEN '1955-1959'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1960 AND 1964 THEN '1960-1964'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1965 AND 1969 THEN '1965-1969'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1970 AND 1974 THEN '1970-1974'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1975 AND 1979 THEN '1975-1979'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1980 AND 1984 THEN '1980-1984'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1985 AND 1989 THEN '1985-1989'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1990 AND 1994 THEN '1990-1994'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 1995 AND 1999 THEN '1995-1999'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2004 THEN '2000-2004'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 2005 AND 2009 THEN '2005-2009'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 2010 AND 2014 THEN '2010-2014'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 2015 AND 2019 THEN '2015-2019'
    WHEN al.release_year BETWEEN 2020 AND 2024 THEN '2020-2024'
    ELSE 'Other'
  END AS year_bucket,
  AVG(ra.rating) AS avg_rating
FROM
  workspace.music.silver_album al
JOIN 
  workspace.music.silver_member_rating ra
ON 
  al.id = ra.album_id
JOIN
  workspace.music.silver_album_club_member acm
ON
  ra.member_id = acm.id
WHERE
  acm.id = :parameter
GROUP BY
  year_bucket
ORDER BY
  year_bucket;

datasets.name: afd2f234
queryLines:
SELECT
  a.name as artist,
  al.name as album,
  al.release_year,
  ra.rating as rating
FROM
  music.silver_album al
    JOIN music.silver_artist a
      ON al.artist_id = a.id
    JOIN music.silver_member_rating ra
      ON al.id = ra.album_id
WHERE ra.member_id = :parameter
ORDER BY
  rating DESC;

datasets.displayName: Club Member Album Details and Insights

datasets.name: 4c0572ad
queryLines:
SELECT
  a.name as artist,
  al.name AS album_name,
  al.release_year
FROM
  workspace.music.silver_album al
    JOIN music.silver_artist a
      ON al.artist_id = a.id
    JOIN workspace.music.silver_member_rating ra
      ON al.id = ra.album_id
WHERE
  ra.album_id NOT IN (
    SELECT
      album_id
    FROM
      workspace.music.silver_member_rating
    WHERE
      member_id = :member_id
  )
GROUP BY
  a.name,
  al.name,
  al.release_year
HAVING
  COUNT(DISTINCT ra.member_id) > 1
ORDER BY
  al.release_year;
